      <title>特朗普解雇举报机构负责人裁定非法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/trump-firing-of-whistleblower-agency-head-unlawful-judge-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名联邦法官裁定，保护政府举报者的一名独立美国机构的负责人上个月被唐纳德·特朗普总统非法开除，即使白宫的目标是将案件置于最高法院。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-02/trump-firing-of-whistleblower-agency-head-unlawful-judge-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Mar 2025 01:43:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列接受我们加沙桥梁造成的计划，而哈马斯巴尔克斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/israel-accepts-us-proposal-for-ramadan-truce-pm-s-office</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列接受了哈马斯balk徒时，接受了美国的新的11小时加沙停火提案，并坚持认为双方在没有派系的情况下实施了一项事实上的战后交易，而没有派系在灾难的飞地中放弃权力或武器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/israel-accepts-us-proposal-for-ramadan-truce-pm-s-office</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 22:22:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄牙总理在反对派的帮助下避免了危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/portugal-prime-minister-says-political-crisis-should-be-avoided</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙总理路易斯·黑山（Luis Montenegro）在试图结束对与一家家族企业有关的潜在利益冲突的猜测之后，从反对派社会主义者那里得到了避免政治危机的帮助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-01/portugal-prime-minister-says-political-crisis-should-be-avoided</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 20:50:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
